*Items on this list may be work in progress*

==Version 0.6==

  * Write a DocumentsOrganizer with clasification by document type, extension, last access, not classified, etc.
  * Write an ApplicationsOrganizer along with an ApplicationsFileListProvider for rpm to show every installed application as one executable file and to let the user drop an rpm file on that folder (as root) to install and delete that file (as root too) to uninstall
  * Create a MultiOrganizer that can use other organizers
  * Create an XML parser to parse configuration of the MultiOrganizer 


==Version 0.8==

  * Create a BeagleSearchFileListProvider
  * Write a MusicOrganizer with clasification by artist, album, genre, etc
  * Define PackageManagerPlugin API for the ApplicationsHandler
  * Extract RedhatPackageManagerPlugin
  * Create a DebianPackageManagerPlugin and possibly others PackageManagerPlugins 


==Version 1.0==

  * Cleanup code
  * gettext support
  * Write documentation 

